fka/Redis)\n    ↓\nAt-least-once delivery (may redeliver on failure)\n    ↓\nConsumer receives event\n    ↓\nIdempotency check (is this already processed?)\n    ↓\nIf duplicate: ACK and exit\n    ↓\nIf new: Execute action + record completion\n    ↓\nCommit"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key requirement"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Every action-taking tool must be idempotent or the agent must dedupe\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exactly-Once (Idempotent At-Least-Once)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Event sent\n    ↓\nAttempt 1: fails\n    ↓\nRetry attempt 2: succeeds\n    ↓\nDeduplication table: \"already processed\"\n    ↓\nSkip duplicate\n    ↓\nResult: Effectively exactly-once"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Implementation"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Implement at-least-once + idempotent operation handlers + proper retry + comprehensive logging\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best Practices for At-Least-Once Systems"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Implement Idempotent Operations"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Technique"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Unique identifiers"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":nu